instruction: Transform this poem into a rap verse.
input:
My love is like a river
That flows to the sea
It is ever-changing
And ever will be
output:
My love is like a river so strong and Divine,
It's ever-changing like the shifting of time.
It's liquid emotions run deep through the night,
My love won't cease no matter what we fight.
I get lost in it's flow, it's Music and light,
The waves of Love run from morning to night.
